'''考平甘島'''（{{thai|t=เกาะเขาพิงกัน|r=Ko Khao Phing Kan}}）是位於[[泰國|泰國]]南部[[攀牙府|攀牙府]]{{link-en|攀牙灣國家公園|Ao Phang Nga National Park}}中的兩個島嶼之統稱。距其40米之外豎立著一個高為20米的島嶼——'''達舖島'''（{{thai|t=เกาะตะปู|r=Ko Tapu}}）。[[詹姆士·龐德系列電影|詹姆士·龐德系列電影]]曾在此拍攝，考平甘島因此被稱為'''007島'''或'''詹姆士·龐德島'''（James Bond Island）。

== 島名由來 ==
考平甘在泰語中意思是「對峙的山」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thaiwaysmagazine.com/phang-nga/phang-nga_attractions_town.html |title=Phang-nga Town |access-date=2014-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100501220723/http://www.thaiwaysmagazine.com/phang-nga/phang-nga_attractions_town.html |archive-date=2010-05-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>其中「考」（Khao）在泰語中是「山」的意思。<ref name=r1>[http://jamesbond.ajb007.co.uk/james-bond-island-thailand/ Approaching James Bond Island] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130831225604/http://jamesbond.ajb007.co.uk/james-bond-island-thailand/ |date=2013-08-31 }}, 6 April 2009</ref>距之不遠的達舖島，其名字「Tapu」在泰語中意為「釘子」，因其像一根釘子直立於海中，故而得名<ref>[http://www.comebesttour.com.tw/eWeb_comebesttour/html/Html_Main.asp?html_fg=phuket3_3 攀牙灣]</ref>。這裡曾是1974年[[007|007]]電影「[[金槍人|金槍人]]」取景地，從此隨著電影聲名大噪，外人多慣稱之為詹姆士·龐德島。而旅遊指南上多將考平甘島稱為詹姆士·龐德島<ref name=r2>Joe Cummings, Becca Blond, Morgan Konn [http://books.google.com/books?id=hh_baRUfbUIC&pg=PA642 Thailand], Lonely Planet (2005) ISBN 1-74059-697-8 p. 642 [http://www.lonelyplanet.com/thailand/andaman-coast/ao-phang-nga-marine-national-park web version]</ref><ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/sunandsea/722953/Thailand-All-quiet-on-the-Andaman-Sea.html Thailand: All quiet on the Andaman Sea], Telegraph.co.uk, 20 November 2000</ref><ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/734375/Time-to-move-on.html Time to move on], Telegraph.co.uk, 18 January 2006</ref><ref name="NZ_Herald_10635289">{{cite news |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/travel/news/article.cfm?c_id=7&objectid=10635289 |title=Phuket: Like a limestone cowboy |author=Sykes, Martin |date=30 March 2010 |work=[[The_New_Zealand_Herald|The New Zealand Herald]] |accessdate=12 October 2011}}</ref><ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/travel/article-1234485/Thailands-Yao-Noi-Island-idyllic-retreat-good-James-Bond-himself.html Thailand's Yao Noi Island, an idyllic retreat good enough for James Bond himself], DailyMail.co.uk, 12 December 2009</ref>（有時也稱呼達舖島為詹姆士·龐德島<ref>[http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27164973/ Travel like 007], Msnbc.com, 11 November 2008</ref>），其原始名稱甚至變得很少使用了。<ref name=b1> Claudia Springer [http://books.google.com/books?id=3wHBIQlLM50C&pg=PA195 James Dean transfigured: the many faces of rebel iconography], University of Texas Press, 2007 ISBN	0292714440 p. 195</ref>

==歷史==
在1974年之前，考平甘島是個很少人訪問的原始地域。1974年，被選為[[007|007]]電影「[[金槍人|金槍人]]」取景地。在影片中，該島是詹姆士·龐德的對頭{{link-en|法蘭西斯哥·史卡拉曼|Francisco Scaramanga}}的棲居地。影片上映後，考平甘島成為一個熱門的景點，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.movie-locations.com/movies/m/mangolden.html |title=The Man With the Golden Gun film locations |access-date=2014-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130324101942/http://www.movie-locations.com/movies/m/mangolden.html |archive-date=2013-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>生活垃圾開始污染該地域。<ref name=b1/>

1981年，考平甘島成為新建立的攀牙灣國家公園中最知名的一個景點。<ref name=r2/>從1998年開始，當地禁止遊客的船隻接近達舖島。出臺這項措施是為了避免該島及其附近的[[石灰岩|石灰岩]]因受到侵蝕而崩塌。<ref>[http://archive.travel.ru/thailand/3742.html Ko Tapu is closed for tourists] {{Wayback|url=http://archive.travel.ru/thailand/3742.html |date=20100106120246 }}, Travel.ru (in Russian)</ref>
